{"tid":795221,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想Upgrade GTX 1060, 我呢隻牛夠唔夠推？","createTime":"2018-08-26T23:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T13:23:40.000Z","uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b648ab43a0eb7e036042a3dbf1c87598afca3ace","tid":795221,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T23:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/072738_4c09b5b7fe7441bc14d9ef9936923d7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F072738_4c09b5b7fe7441bc14d9ef9936923d7d.png&h=8832c81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原先用緊GTX 950<br />\n睇Spec話最少400W, 咁我呢隻係咪已經夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63104052a2d65d1c6085e88da1e1b69c4199110","tid":795221,"uid":166670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T23:40:39.000Z","msg":"用到 放心"},{"pid":"8366ddd93f4f183b391e4cc4588d3db8fc6a7c08","tid":795221,"uid":173741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:03:31.000Z","msg":"450w都夠"},{"pid":"b5fb00fea5365f153fee4deab491d5ed127e0366","tid":795221,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:08:11.000Z","msg":"夠"},{"pid":"50fd93185d343ee6ed4802df25776e7619bc1e46","tid":795221,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:44:58.000Z","msg":"1060有免外部電源版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49406eaf3b8850632ba83460be24edd02b687613","tid":795221,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:59:33.000Z","msg":"水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573ebab46c114f4c7e0e983ffb6d484afad934c4","tid":795221,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:05:40.000Z","msg":"等新gpu la"},{"pid":"20e7672f2d37ae3ea4064a98871a30a60d6c57a3","tid":795221,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"鍾意信就信，唔信就算<br />\n<br />\n其實呢隻野報大數，得435W，睇睇張Label<br />\n入面仲要得360W 12V<br />\n用耐咗老化，估你用咗兩三年左右，要打多個8-9折<br />\n280-320W左右<br />\n<br />\n而家基本所有hardware<br />\n除咗主機板一部份，同2.5既HDD，SSD<br />\n全部都用12V<br />\n一張1060都120W<br />\r\nCPU 80W<br />\n<br />\n未計主機板用咗幾多12V<br />\n12V得返80-120W 比其他東西用<br />\n<br />\n一把大食少少既12cm風扇都10W，8cm 5W左右<br />\n一般人都係當主機板12V + 5V 會用30W左右<br />\nRAM 一條5W<br />\n<br />\n悲觀少少計<br />\n當一前一後12cm扇<br />\nCPU散熱用原裝，計一把8cm扇<br />\n主機板一堆東西全部由12V供電<br />\nRAM 2條<br />\n<br />\n12V得返15W，其實好搏下<br />\n邊部份估少咗，或者隻牛再老化多少少就會出事<br />\n<br />\n隻牛本來就雞雞地，供電唔多穩<br />\n再扯盡佢會點，自己Google睇下"},{"pid":"293ef81cba4b49876164e410366b44de6fef84d5","tid":795221,"uid":193026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"順帶一提，除咗風扇之外<br />\n各樣件愈靚，愈近個估計既數<br />\n超頻件應該直頭過埋個數<br />\n<br />\n另外，老化程度睇Full load得幾密，同散熱有無數好<br />\n一般計Server長期full load法同散熱，3年7折左右"},{"pid":"74f1040e1bf0bd3a2698885c9f98a6f24525882b","tid":795221,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"293ef81cba4b49876164e410366b44de6fef84d5","tid":795221,"uid":193026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"順帶一提，除咗風扇之外<br />\n各樣件愈靚，愈近個估計既數<br />\n超頻件應該直頭過埋個數<br />\n<br />\n另外，老化程度睇Full load得幾密，同散熱有無數好<br />\n一般計Server長期full load法同散熱，3年7折左右"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:01:05.000Z","msg":"以下配件應該唔算好食電？<br />\n風扇x1<br />\n100GB SSD<br />\n1TB Harddisk<br />\n16gb ram x1<br />\nCPU係i5 6500<br />\n<br />\n硬件野一知半解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  求錫教<br />\n全部用左接近兩年"},{"pid":"66a5a0f6b71e57cae13146ff74f15b75ba41d73f","tid":795221,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"q